{{ComponentStats:sc.fiji:Gray_Morphology}}This plugin performs [[wikipedia:Mathematical morphology|mathematical morphology]] on grayscale images. It only works on [[8-bit]] grayscale images.

For more information on morphological operators in image processing, have a look at [http://homepages.inf.ed.ac.uk/rbf/HIPR2/matmorph.htm this page].

See also [https://imagej.net/plugins/gray-morphology.html Gray Morphology at the ImageJ 1.x website].

